‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ PortalReceiptsApp_v1.0.0_Release.zip   # Complete release package
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ PortalReceiptsApp_v1.0.0_Release/      # Unpacked release folder
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ PortalReceiptsApp_Setup_v1.0.0.exe
